  <summary>4/14/1999--Introduced.
Kosova Self-Defense Act of 1999 - Declares it is U.S. policy to provide the interim government of Kosova with the capability to defend and protect the Kosovar population against armed aggression. Authorizes appropriations for grants to such government to be used for training and support for the established self-defense forces to carry out such policy.</summary>
